article_id:2052,category_name:Maintenance,title_name:Regarding Maintenance on March 24(PT) [Addendum],image_path:,message:<div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1616641200"></span>]</strong></span><br>The maintenance is now complete.<br><br>As a token of our appreciation for your patience, we will send the following items to all players who started playing before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1616598000"></span>.<br><br>・Exquisite Honey x20<br>・Blessed Ethon Ashes x20<br><br>These items can be claimed from your goodie box for up to 7 days after reception.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div><div><br></div><hr><div>We will be performing maintenance during the following period to update the servers and prepare for the release of Version 2.6.0. Please note that you will not be able to obtain rewards from quests that are completed during the maintenance period.</div><div><br></div><div>■Maintenance Period</div><div>Around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1616598000"></span> to around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1616641200"></span></div><div><br></div><div>■Notes</div><div>1. You will not be able to play Dragalia Lost during maintenance.</div><div>2. Maintenance may start and/or end before or after the scheduled times.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1616047200,update_time1616641227